<pre class="content" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Technically, add apparmor=1 security=apparmor to kernelopts.
qvm-prefs -s vmname kernelopts "nopat apparmor=1 security=apparmor"
For Debian templates I don't foresee any issues. For Whonix...</pre>

